  "text": "Find all WebIDL interface files under dom/webidl/ for Fetch API (Request, Response, Headers, FetchEvent) and corresponding C++ binding implementations under dom/fetch/. The WebIDL files define the Web-facing interfaces: Request.webidl, Response.webidl, Headers.webidl, FetchEvent.webidl, and Fetch.webidl. The C++ implementations live in dom/fetch/ with Request.h/.cpp, Response.h/.cpp, Headers.h/.cpp backed by Internal* classes (InternalRequest, InternalResponse, InternalHeaders). FetchEvent is implemented in dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerEvents.h/.cpp. FetchDriver orchestrates the actual fetch operation.",
